('135', '1', '2011-11-24 08:41:50', '2011-11-24 08:41:50', '<div id=\"lipsum\">\r\n\r\nGenesis Rawai Co.,Ltd is a project developer, owning and developing residential housing in key areas in Phuket, Thailand.¬† Currently manages and employs 120 staff and contractors across Phuket. Combining unparalleled experience, comprehensive capabilities across all industries and business functions, and extensive research on Thailand‚Äôs most successful construction companies, Genesis Rawai Co.,Ltd collaborates with customers to help them acquire valued property with a great return on investment.\r\n\r\nOur \"high performance business\" strategy builds on our expertise in construction, consulting, technology and outsourcing to help us build developments and projects at the highest levels so they can create sustainable value for our customers. Using our industry knowledge, service-offering expertise and technology capabilities, we identify new business and construction trends and develop solutions to help our customers from around the world:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>New construction ideas and technologies.</li>\r\n	<li>Increasing cost efficiency in existing projects.</li>\r\n	<li>Improving operational performance.</li>\r\n	<li>Manage our projects more effectively and efficiently.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have extensive relationships with Thailand‚Äôs leading companies and the Thai government and work with all relevant government departments ‚Äî including the local planning departments, Land offices, Business Development Departments and the Revenue Departments. Our commitment to customer satisfaction strengthens and extends our relationships. For example, existing customers refer us to their friends.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAmong the many strengths that distinguish Genesis Rawai Co.,Ltd in the marketplace are our:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Extensive industry expertise.</li>\r\n	<li>Broad and evolving construction ideas.</li>\r\n	<li>Expertise in managing projects.</li>\r\n	<li>History of technology innovation and implementation, including new construction techniques and weather and climate resistant materials.</li>\r\n	<li>Commitment to the long-term development of our employees and partners.</li>\r\n	<li>Proven and experienced management team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur Core Values have shaped the culture and defined the character of our company, guiding how we behave and make decisions:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Stewardship:</em> Building a heritage for future generations, acting with an owner mentality, developing people and projects everywhere we are, and meeting our commitments to all internal and external satisfaction.</li>\r\n	<li><em>Best People:</em> Attracting and developing the best talent for our business, stretching our people and developing a \"can do\" attitude.</li>\r\n	<li><em>Customer Value Creation:</em> Improving our customers\' property value for money, creating long-term, win-win relationships and focusing on execution excellence.</li>\r\n	<li><em>One Main Network:</em> Mobilizing the power of teaming to deliver consistently exceptional service to our customers anywhere.</li>\r\n	<li><em>Respect for the Individual:</em> Valuing diversity, ensuring an interesting and inclusive environment, and treating people as we would like to be treated ourselves.</li>\r\n	<li><em>Integrity:</em> Inspiring trust by taking responsibility, acting ethically, and encouraging honest and open debate.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBy enhancing our managing and outsourcing expertise with alliances and other capabilities, we help move customers forward in every part of owning a new house, from strategic planning, day-to-day operations to final handover of key and paperwork. With approximately 120 people serving customers all over Phuket, deep industry and business process expertise, broad and evolving construction ideas and a proven track record, Genesis Rawai Co.,Ltd can mobilize the right people, skills and technologies to help customers improve their experience and get the best house in the best project.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Who are we ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'who-we-are', '', '', '2012-01-05 06:01:42', '2012-01-05 06:01:42', '', '13', 'http://www.genesisvilla.com/?page_id=135', '0', 'page', '', '0'),
